<HEAD>Communists Claim Responsibility for U.S. Officer's Killing</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto NY7</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By CLARO CORTES</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
