<FIRST>r i AM-Honduras     04-22 0291</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Honduras,0302</SECOND>
<HEAD>President Says Capital Flight Damaging Honduras; Pleads For Money
Return</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By FREDDY CUEVAS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>TEGUCIGALPA, Honduras (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
